data.description:
Discover the perfect urban living in Minneapolis with this updated duplex, conveniently located near
downtown, Target Field, and a variety of restaurants and breweries. Modern amenities and stylish finishes
make this property a comfortable retreat. Embrace an exciting lifestyle, whether you're a sports
enthusiast, foodie, or craft beer lover. With its prime location, this duplex offers an excellent
opportunity to experience the city's dynamic atmosphere firsthand. Don't miss out on owning this gem in
the heart of Minneapolis!
